    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Regions in one country that are controlled by another country or power. An example of a historical controlled region was when the Dutch controlled Taiwan in the 17th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
